Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:34.99,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,That's not right, Kirsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.28,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Play it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.63,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Hold the pedal a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:42.00,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,That's what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:45.23,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Play it with a little more emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.13,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:49.62,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.14,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Try and grasp the form for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.46,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Just the form?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:56.25,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Feelings and form are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:57.81,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,I know that mu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.57,0:01:07.17,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Listen, Kirsi. Once you grasp the feel of it, your emotions will be able to flow freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:12.92,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,For example, if you smile when you're sad, your sadness will lessen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:17.22,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you're saying, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:21.10,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Maybe that analogy was a little too difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:24.59,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,She talks like an adult, but she's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.59,0:01:26.77,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a child, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:33.05,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.28,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Sensei, is there a full moon out tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:39.41,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:41.60,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.09,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Of course I am, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.08,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,I like this light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:54.33,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,I can't see it, but I can feel its silver glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.20,Location,,0,0,0,,{\c&H172617&\fnArial}plane crash
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:20.53,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Are you sure the people looking for us are already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:23.95,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,It was information from above, so keep your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:28.70,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Geez. We've become popular, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:30.24,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Do you have any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.24,0:02:33.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:36.64,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Yin's unreliable, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.87,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,She can't even fulfill her only purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:53.94,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Number Six's lips look discolored to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:57.20,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Increase the sodium concentration by point zero-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:00.08,DTB-Default,Assistant A,0,0,0,,Everything is going according to standard procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:06.33,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Recognize the differences between them, and don't rely so much on monitors and instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:10.06,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,They're delicate in body and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.63,DTB-Default,Assistant A,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.94,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:23.80,DTB-Default,Assistant A,0,0,0,,No. His lips seemed to move, as if he was talking in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.58,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,He might have been seeing a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:28.02,DTB-Default,Assistant A,0,0,0,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.31,DTB-Default,Assistant A,0,0,0,,But mediums...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:34.53,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Just kidding. I know it's been proven that they don't dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.14,0:03:38.83,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Then again, maybe they can experience it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:40.44,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,A sweet dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:47.60,DTB-Default,Assistant B,0,0,0,,Chief Ishizaki, there are some changes in the observer apparitions currently on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.22,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Contractors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.50,DTB-Default,Assistant B,0,0,0,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:57.75,DTB-Default,Assistant B,0,0,0,,Several are gathering near a specific coordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:21.82,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,I thought I told you not to go out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.35,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.81,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Well, it looked like he was spying on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.84,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,One of our targets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.38,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.04,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,He might have been from a higher level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:45.56,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Let me remind you that our job is to identify their numbers, identities, and abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.56,0:04:46.83,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,We're not supposed to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.95,DTB-Default,Assistant A,0,0,0,,It's an emergency! The mediums are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.82,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.26,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,Retrieve the observer apparitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:17.97,DTB-Default,Assistant B,0,0,0,,About that... They're not returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.70,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.03,DTB-Default,Assistant B,0,0,0,,The only explanation I can think of is that they might have been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:22.88,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,How about the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.90,DTB-Default,Assistant B,0,0,0,,Activity in CY-463.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:30.64,DTB-Default,Kanami,0,0,0,,A contractor that can capture observer apparitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.15,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,How pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.27,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:46.07,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,My mind suddenly synced with a doll that sent out an observer apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.90,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It isn't a good feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.11,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,You're still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.88,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,This is too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:11.03,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It looks like I was able to establish a connection with one of our targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:26.07,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you were able to see her in this picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.36,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You want me to find this girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:31.64,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Understand? Can you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:34.74,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Please take the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:38.31,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:43.75,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,But Mr. Foreigner, um... Mr. Kashite... Kashite... Kashite...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.82,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kastinen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.28,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Eelis Kastinen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:49.90,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Oh, Kastenee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.00,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You've come to the right place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:58.61,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,A famous pianist like yourself, coming all the way from Scandinavia to hire me, Kurasawa Gai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:07:03.03,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were well-known overseas, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.47,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Gai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.74,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Yes, Gai Kurasawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.42,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Japanese most famous detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.28,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.16,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Gai... Gai Kurasawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:22.90,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I've been saying that I'm Gai, Gai Kurasawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:24.54,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Does the name sound familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.95,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,You're relatively calm about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.16,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,You've identified the target, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.60,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to make your move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:41.96,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Don't panic. It isn't difficult to lure a doll out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:46.85,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,If it hasn't recovered from last night's incident, it'll just wander about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:49.36,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,as if it was sleep-walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.20,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,You're all set, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.24,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,By the way, do you have any cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:57.10,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Is it okay for you to smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.20,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Aren't you supposed to be a singer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.35,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,That's a mean way of saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:06.15,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I stood on the stage of Volksoper a long time ago, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:08.53,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,I was one of many, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.50,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It's a problem if I run out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.41,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,since it's my remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.39,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,What are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:20.89,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:28.05,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,"A maiden stands still by the lake in the midnight sun, falling into the bright night alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:32.82,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,"The blank, cold, silver moon, her only companion."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.94,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,That's my remuneration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:39.59,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,An elegant one, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:43.57,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Not bad. It's a little too feminine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:45.92,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It'd be better if you made it rhyme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.55,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Don't look into it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.55,0:08:50.80,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,I've never written a poem in my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.58,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,until I became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:57.93,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Isn't that great? You still have a soul capable of functioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.21,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,even if it is someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:06.59,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to contact Yin since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.40,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Does that mean she escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:12.25,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's no way a doll could act on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:16.78,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,She's only been programmed with enough information necessary to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:18.74,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What else could have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:22.00,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,One of the syndicate's men was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.91,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,This occurred last night as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.90,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Was it the work of the group that infiltrated the area?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.69,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:32.15,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that Yin was abducted by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:32.78,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Abducted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.51,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,In an effort to acquire information about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:40.15,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,She doesn't have any emotions, but unfortunately for us, she has a great memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.50,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,The syndicate was aware of it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.10,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.10,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,They've also been keeping tabs on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.50,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,You better be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.40,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,If worst comes to worst, dispose of the doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:05.02,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,Hey, you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.45,DTB-Default,Man,0,0,0,,What's with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.75,DTB-Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Forget about it. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.56,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.60,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,She hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.56,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Shit! It's that clumsy detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.43,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,She's not here, as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:43.49,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,We're going to ask questions around here, Kiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.04,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.55,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,"Ncha"? You're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.58,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you I was going to take the rest of the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:54.44,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I'm meeting a friend. I only tagged along because it was on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.09,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.68,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.40,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Investigator? That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.58,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:06.93,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He's looking for Yin for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:10.31,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,I see. Let me know if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.66,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Are you saying I should follow him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:13.40,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,He knows what I look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.02,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,You have an ordinary appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:21.22,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:37.69,Title,,0,0,0,,Episode Thirteen A Heart Unswaying on the Water's Surface... (Part One)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.41,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,That was wonderful, Kirsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.89,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Next, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.07,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:36.03,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,No, I just dropped my penlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.16,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, let me turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:38.98,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.47,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,No, I like things as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.30,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,I like this light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.17,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,The moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.07,DTB-Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.10,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,It's all right. I think it's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:10.13,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,Did you find the penlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.20,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:13.49,DTB-Default,Kirsi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:33.72,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,Who do they think they're trying to fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.82,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,The character was completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:38.64,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I can't let that writer live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:40.73,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I'm going to write his name in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.24,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,Geez, even though the artwork was amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:46.00,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,That's why they shouldn't make adaptations in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.71,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,You're kidding me... It's that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:57.61,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Refills are free, so you don't have to drink sparingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.50,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,You look gloomy. Is that part of your character?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.39,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Take my advice and try to smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:09.64,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:12.65,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.01,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,Cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.14,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:20.48,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,See? That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.96,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,First of all, you have to establish your external features,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.74,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,whether it's for cosplay or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.99,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Cosplay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:31.88,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.15,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,Bring me some coffee on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.33,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Get it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.99,0:14:38.36,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.77,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.85,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Which family restaurant is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.10,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Isn't there something that I'd recognize around there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:04.37,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,What don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:07.18,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,There's an anime shop on the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.70,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.45,DTB-Default,Mayuko,0,0,0,,We're splitting the bill, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.50,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,You were lured by your own observer apparition,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:37.26,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,just as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.87,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,You lost sight of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.39,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.79,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,T-That way, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.95,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:48.15,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:53.04,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,I can read a doll's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.41,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.42,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.51,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Run, Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:11.95,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.26,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.81,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,W-What the... ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:25.49,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Watch out, Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:32.07,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,It's falling down! Hei, run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:35.45,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.73,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Get as far away as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:54.49,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.43,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:02.93,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Kirsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:09.56,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Bertha, were you trying to get me killed, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.44,DTB-Default,Itzhak,0,0,0,,Bertha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:20.20,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm not swallowing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:22.95,DTB-Default,Bertha,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you this was my remuneration?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.00,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi, it's me, Eelis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.04,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Eelis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:32.09,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,That's right. Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:51.52,DTB-Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,Yes. Investigations are currently underway, but it will take some time to determine the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.52,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Hide her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:54.56,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Only until she's able to leave the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.88,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:18:00.41,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I don't want to impose, but why was she there in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:03.22,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.16,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,I only know she was being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.83,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Chased?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.89,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.44,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,She wouldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.07,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Definitely a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.63,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:17.66,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Listen, it's already become a huge story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:19.40,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.99,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Chasing such a cute girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:24.96,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Kirsi-chan, you should stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.39,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I want to dress you up in...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.90,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.77,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,This isn't a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.90,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,You'll be handsomely compensated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:38.16,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I have no choice, since we're already in the same predicament.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.61,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,That aside, where can we hide her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:42.49,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,A hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.95,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,There has to be at least one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.84,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "at least one"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:49.32,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Everyone's looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.79,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.21,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,Kiko will do her best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.84,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:00.62,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Not only did you lose sight of the enemy, but you also lost Yin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.47,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,What's your excuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:08.40,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,The next time you see Yin, kill her, regardless of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.82,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Huang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:14.86,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,Don't you think we'll be playing into the enemy's hand if we become disorganized now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:20.01,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Disorganized? I'm not your ally, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.36,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't treat me as one of your own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.82,DTB-Default,Mao,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.54,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. We don't regard you as one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:35.92,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Contractors like us don't possess emotions that would make us tremble in fear like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.53,DTB-Default,Hei,0,0,0,,Fortunately enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:43.97,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Don't be so arrogant! You don't know how frightening the syndicate can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:49.29,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,Kill Yin, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:52.35,DTB-Default,Huang,0,0,0,,If you won't, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:06.45,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,Why did you have to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:10.13,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,It'd be unfair if you went without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.33,DTB-Default,Gai,0,0,0,,I'm their bodyguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.71,DTB-Default,Kiko,0,0,0,,I was the one who suggested a hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.42,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Kirsi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.21,0:20:22.22,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Let's go back once everything settles down, Kirsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.22,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:28.10,DTB-Default,Kastinen,0,0,0,,Yes, back to our homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:32.81,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.90,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.75,0:20:44.00,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The train never had a destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:48.88,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The drizzling rain reveals a secret crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.88,0:20:52.20,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,An unwavering heart, a resolute mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.38,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,You cannot be hurt any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:21:00.18,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,Are the days that have disappeared with the moonlight asking for atonement?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:05.26,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The light she felt in the past cannot reach her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:09.25,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,542)}Episode Fourteen A Heart Unswaying on the Water's Surface... (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.71,DTB-Default,Yin,0,0,0,,The light will radiate.